prompts.prompt: Create a full stack app that requires users to login in order to access the app. The signup login screen should be one all black with the login and signup fields in the center of the screen. Once the user logs in, they are redirected to an image upload gallery that sorts photos by upload date, newest first. Photos should have the ability for a user to upvote once. Photos should be in a container with no borders and no gaps between containers. In order for the user to access the site, they must submit a valid email address, which will receive a code for initial verification.
